TITLE: Initializing Javalin with Configuration Options
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to create a new Javalin instance with various configuration options. It showcases the main configuration categories available in Javalin.
SOURCE: https://github.com/javalin/website/blob/master/pages/docs/docs-past-5-6-x.md#2025-04-08_snippet_31

LANGUAGE: java
