TITLE: Logback XML Configuration for Javalin Applications
DESCRIPTION: Comprehensive Logback configuration file with console and file appenders, including pattern layouts, rolling file policies, and log level settings for Javalin applications.
SOURCE: https://github.com/javalin/website/blob/master/_posts/tutorials/community/2023-07-30-javalin-logging.md#2025-04-08_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: xml
