TITLE: Configuring Log4j2 XML Configuration for Javalin Applications
DESCRIPTION: Sample log4j2.xml configuration file that sets up console and file appenders for logging. It defines log patterns with color support for console output and configures rolling file appender with size-based rotation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/javalin/website/blob/master/_posts/tutorials/community/2023-07-30-javalin-logging.md#2025-04-08_snippet_8

LANGUAGE: xml
CODE:
