SOURCE: https://github.com/javalin/website/blob/master/_posts/tutorials/2020-01-18-javalin-testing-example.md#2025-04-08_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: java
CODE:
```
public static void create(Context ctx) {
    String username = ctx.queryParam("username");
    if (username == null || username.length() < 5) {
        throw new BadRequestResponse();
    } else {
        users.add(username);
        ctx.status(201);
    }
}
```

