TITLE: GitHub Actions Configuration for Multi-Platform Java CI
DESCRIPTION: GitHub Actions workflow configuration that tests multiple Java versions across Windows, MacOS, and Ubuntu platforms using matrix strategy.
SOURCE: https://github.com/javalin/website/blob/master/_posts/blog/2019-11-03-moving-from-travis-to-github-actions.md#2025-04-08_snippet_2

